Date: Tue, 24 May 2016 18:19:59 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 0236/1345] net: mvpp2x: use relaxed read/write function in
 tx/rx functions and mv_pp22_thread_relaxed_read
 in mv_pp22_poll

commit  34b6807476b632b72d20a95d14d9e59c96bb394b from
https://github.com/MarvellEmbeddedProcessors/linux-marvell.git

